想問下值唔值"},{"pid":"629b6820d87f4d8282c2dce4421367ac71defc71","tid":240192,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"Fb 好似有啲倉鼠領養group <br />\n天竺鼠又唔同性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢地全部都好乖好得意"},{"pid":"4a31fc73d2ff60744553b09cd82a2e32b8939f64","tid":240192,"uid":104821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fb 好似有啲倉鼠領養group <br />\n天竺鼠又唔同性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢地全部都好乖好得意</blockquote><br />\n有時想領養。但係等左成個月都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底應唔應該等領養。。<br />\n有時等到幾秒後又比人領養"},{"pid":"b211e6d6acf8dd91c80cfade604d53bef3ea6e8d","tid":240192,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寵物店咪有囉 你想點接觸</blockquote><br />\nLIHKG唔係推領養嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主問點接觸咋嘛 又唔係買 去睇吓玩吓先 係養咪上網搵人放</blockquote><br />\n見到有天竺鼠領養，但係要比500領養費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想問下值唔值</blockquote><br />\n幾百蚊好似都差唔多 但真係最好你入咗啲fb group睇多啲人講有乜要注意先 始終未養過 我之前有養過天竺 天竺會叫架 你要唔好嫌嘈"},{"pid":"930ef0672940fcba2239efcd5108a216595e6eb8","tid":240192,"uid":104664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Fb 好似有啲倉鼠領養group <br />\n天竺鼠又唔同性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢地全部都好乖好得意</blockquote><br />\n有時想領養。但係等左成個月都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底應唔應該等領養。。<br />\n有時等到幾秒後又比人領養</blockquote><br />\n我係唔鍾意領養既人 因為期待落空好討厭 不過我明白大多數人都推薦領養係有原因既 同埋喺你等既期間咪做吓功課先 了解足夠先開始養好啲"},{"pid":"3b08f733ba39ac779214de278fd5228b00e813f9","tid":240192,"uid":104821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Fb 好似有啲倉鼠領養group <br />\n天竺鼠又唔同性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢地全部都好乖好得意</blockquote><br />\n有時想領養。但係等左成個月都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底應唔應該等領養。。<br />\n有時等到幾秒後又比人領養</blockquote><br />\n我係唔鍾意領養既人 因為期待落空好討厭 不過我明白大多數人都推薦領養係有原因既 同埋喺你等既期間咪做吓功課先 了解足夠先開始養好啲</blockquote><br />\n所以好希望各巴絲分享下飼養心得同總結下設備。感覺好少post講鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2275eb897e445d2b1a5c55f091b752a5477e9f92","tid":240192,"uid":106233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"我有兩仔兩女天竺鼠, 兩個月左右<br />\n可以領養"},{"pid":"2f79bcc00fe029c238ec3bf26c71aa2204b25fb1","tid":240192,"uid":104821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有兩仔兩女天竺鼠, 兩個月左右<br />\n可以領養</blockquote><br />\n有興趣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2034d631771a7bc7965447ac26e394eaaea382f4","tid":240192,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"倉鼠得兩年命仔，喊死你"},{"pid":"f39eb822c6997bfdfacc38d2d37e946149f2ce29","tid":240192,"uid":106233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有兩仔兩女天竺鼠, 兩個月左右<br />\n可以領養</blockquote><br />\n有興趣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我4隻都係全啡, 只係有d 細節位唔同色<br />\n巴打本身有冇養其他野?<br />\n同埋照顧佢地都要好花心機下, <br />\n因為佢地要係咁食草, 食住柯, 屎尿極多<br />\n每一早要搞最少半個鐘掃屎同換尿布<br />\n每晚大清潔最少1個鐘"},{"pid":"6ca2c5b387a0b7a5cf62aaad91abb050341c1fd8","tid":240192,"uid":104821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有兩仔兩女天竺鼠, 兩個月左右<br />\n可以領養</blockquote><br />\n有興趣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我4隻都係全啡, 只係有d 細節位唔同色<br />\n巴打本身有冇養其他野?<br />\n同埋照顧佢